@startuml
title Choose Discount Offer and Add to Basket

actor Customer as C
boundary System as S
control OfferService as OS
entity Basket as B

C -> S: View discount offers
S -> OS: Fetch available discount offers
OS --> S: List of discount offers
S --> C: Display list of discount offers

C -> S: Choose discount offer (offerId)
S -> OS: Get discount offer details(offerId)
OS --> S: Discount offer details
S --> C: Display discount offer details

C -> S: Click "Add to basket" (offerId)
S -> OS: Check availability(offerId)
OS --> S: availableCount

alt [availableCount > 0]
  S -> B: Insert discount offer into basket (offerId)
  B --> S: Insert confirmation
  S --> C: Show "Offer added to basket"
else [availableCount == 0]
  S --> C: Show "Offer unavailable"
end

@enduml